\c 46
\s Jakove anoenda Egipita
\p
\v 1 Zvino Israeri akabva nezvose zvaakange anazvo, akasvika Bheerishebha, akabayira Mwari wababa vake Isaka zvibayiro.
\v 2 Mwari akataura naIsraeri nezviratidzo usiku, akati, Jakove ! Jakove ! Iye akati, Ndiri pano hangu.
\v 3 Akati, Ndini Mwari, iye Mwari wababa vako; usatya hako kuburukira Egipita; nekuti ndichakuita rudzi rukuru ikoko;
\v 4 ndichaburukira Egipita newe, ndigokudzosazve zvirokwazvo; Josefa uchaisa ruoko rwake pachiso chako.
\p
\v 5 Jakove akasimuka, akabva Bheerishebha; vanakomana vaIsraeri vakatakura Jakove baba vavo, navana vavo vaduku, navakadzi vavo, nengoro dzakanga dzatumwa naFarao kuti dzivatakure.
\p
\v 6 Vakatora mombe dzavo nenhumbi dzavo dzavakange vawana munyika yeKenani, vakasvika Egipita, Jakove navanakomana vake vose pamwechete naye;
\p
\v 7 vanakomana vake, navana vavanakomana vake pamwechete naye, navakunda vake, navakunda vavanakomana vake, navose vorudzi rwake, vakaenda navo Egipita.
\p
\v 8 Ndiwo mazita avana vaIsraeri vakasvika Egipita: Jakove, navanakomana vake, vachiti: Rubheni, dangwe raJakobho.
\v 9 Navanakomana vaRubheni: Hanoki, naParu, naHezironi, Karami.
\v 10 Navanakomana vaSimioni: Jemueri, naJamini, naOhadhi, naJakini, naZohari, naShauri, waiva mwanakomana womukadzi weKenani.
\v 11 Navanakomana vaRevhi: Gerishoni, naKohati, naMerari.
\v 12 Navanakomana vaJudha: Eri, naOnani, naShera, naPerezi, naZera; asi Zera naOnani vakafira panyika yeKenani. Vanakomana vaPerezi vaiva Hezironi, naHamori.
\v 13 Navanakomana vaIsakari: Tora, naPuwa, naJobho, naShimuroni.
\v 14 Navanakomana vaZebhuroni: Seredhi, naEroni, naJareeri.
\v 15 Ndivo vanakomana vaRea, vaakaberekera Jakove paPadhanaramu, nomukunda wake Dhina; vanakomana vake navakunda vake vose vaiva vanhu vana makumi matatu navatatu.
\p
\v 16 Navanakomana vaGadhi: Zifioni, naHagi, naShumi, naEzibhoni, naEri, naArodhi, naAreri.
\v 17 Navanakomana vaAsheri: Imuna, naIshivha, naIshivhi, naBheria, naSera, hanzvadzi yavo; navanakomana vaBhiriha vaiva Hebheri, naMakieri.
\v 18 Ndivo vanakomana vaZiripa, Rabhani waakapa Rea, mukunda wake; akaberekera Jakove vanhu ava vane gumi navatanhatu.
\p
\v 19 Vanakomana vaRakeri, mukadzi waJakove, vaiva Josefa naBhenjamini.
\v 20 Josefa akaberekerwa Manase naEfuremu panyika yeEgipita, ndivo vaakaberekerwa naAsenati, mukunda waPotifari, mupristi weOni.
\v 21 Navanakomana vaBhenjamini: Bhera, naBhekeri, naAshibheri naGera, naNaamani, naEhi, naRoshi, naMupimi, naHupimi, naAdhi.
\v 22 Ndivo vanakomana vaRakeri, vakaberekerwa Jakove; vose vaiva vane gumi navana.
\p
\v 23 Navanakomana vaDhani: Hushimi.
\v 24 Navanakomana vaNafutari: Jazeeri, naGuni, naJezeri, naShiremi.
\v 25 Ndivo vanakomana vaBhiriha, Rabhani waakapa Rakeri, mukunda wake; ndivo vaakaberekera Jakove; vose vaiva vanomwe.
\p
\v 26 Zvino vanhu vose vakauya naJakobho Egipita, vakange vabuda pachiuno chake, vakadzi vavanakomana vaJakove vasingaverengwi, vose vaiva vanhu vana makumi matanhatu navatanhatu.
\v 27 Vanakomana vaJosefa vaakange aberekerwa Egipita vaiva vanhu vaviri; vose veimba yaJakove vakauya Egipita, vaiva vanhu vana makumi manomwe.
\p
\v 28 Akatuma Judha pamberi pake kuna Josefa kuti amuratidze nzira inoenda Gosheni.
\v 29 Ipapo Josefa akagadzira ngoro yake, akakwira Gosheni, kundosangana naIsraeri, baba vake; akazvizivisa kwavari, akawira pamutsipa wavo, akachema pamutsipa wavo nguva huru.
\v 30 Israeri akati kuna Josefa, Zvino ngandichifa hangu, nekuti ndaona chiso chako, kuti uchiri mupenyu.
\p
\v 31 Zvino Josefa akati kuvana vababa vake naveimba yababa vake, Ini ndichakwira kundoudza Farao, ndichiti kwaari, Vana vababa vangu, naveimba yababa vangu, vaigara kunyika yeKenani, vasvika kwandiri;
\v 32 varume ava vafudzi, nekuti vaipfuwa zvipfuwo; vauya namakwai avo, nemombe dzavo, nezvose zvavanazvo.
\v 33 Zvino kana modanwa naFarao, akati, Basa renyu nderei?
\v 34 Muti, Varanda venyu vaiva vapfuwi vezvipfuwo kubva paucheche hwedu kusvikira zvino, isu namadzibaba edu; kuti mugare munyika yeGosheni, nekuti vafudzi vose vanonyangadza vaEgipita.
